originalText.text:
World's Best Wedding Planners!
Yesse and Natalia and extremely experienced, bilingual, detail-oriented, supportive, amazing wedding planners! They helped me with all the big things and details-especially the things I hadn't thought of before! Additionally, whatever service I needed, they were able to recommend someone, so that was a huge help, and saved us money too!
They even created a second huge bouquet of flowers to post on our wedding arbor, and you couldn't even tell which one was the more expensive one from the florist, and which one was homemade by Natalia and Yesse! They are very talented and will make your big day beautiful!
